#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/wine/_index.adoc:138
#, no-wrap
msgid "Commercial WINE Implementations"
msgstr "商业 WINE 的实施"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/wine/_index.adoc:142
msgid ""
"A number of companies have taken WINE and made it a core of their own, proprietary products (WINE's LGPL license "
"permits this).  Two of the most famous of these are as follows:"
msgstr ""
"许多公司已经采用了 WINE ，并使其成为他们自己专有产品的核心（ WINE 的 LGPL 许可证允许这样做）。如下是其中最著名的两"
"个："

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/wine/_index.adoc:144
msgid "Codeweavers CrossOver"
msgstr "Codeweavers CrossOver"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/wine/_index.adoc:147
msgid ""
"This solution provides a simplified \"one-click\" installation of WINE, which contains additional enhancements and "
"optimizations (although the company contributes many of these back upstream to the WINE project).  One area of "
"focus for Codeweavers is to make the most popular applications install and run smoothly."
msgstr ""
"这个解决方案提供了一个简化的“一键式”WINE安装，它包含了额外的增强和优化功能（尽管该公司将其中许多功能回馈给WINE项目"
"的上游）。Codeweavers 的一个重点领域是使最流行的应用程序能够顺利安装和运行。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/wine/_index.adoc:150
msgid ""
"While the company once produced a native FreeBSD version of their CrossOver solution, it appears to have long been "
"abandoned.  While some resources (such as a https://www.codeweavers.com/compatibility/crossover/forum/"
"freebsd[dedicated forum]) are still present, they also have seen no activity for some time."
msgstr ""
"虽然该公司曾经为他们的 CrossOver 解决方案制作了一个原生的 FreeBSD 版本，但它似乎早已被放弃了。虽然一些资源（如 "
"https://www.codeweavers.com/compatibility/crossover/forum/freebsd[dedicated forum] ）仍然存在，但它们也有一段时间没"
"有活动了。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/wine/_index.adoc:152
msgid "Steam Proton"
msgstr "Steam Proton"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/wine/_index.adoc:155
msgid ""
"Gaming company Steam also uses WINE to enable Windows(R) games to install and run on other systems.  it is primary "
"target is Linux-based systems, though some support exists for macOS as well."
msgstr ""
"游戏公司 Steam 也使用 WINE 使 Windows(R) 游戏能够在其他系统上安装和运行。它的主要目标是基于 Linux 的系统，尽管对 "
"macOS 也存在一些支持。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/wine/_index.adoc:157
msgid ""
"While Steam does not offer a native FreeBSD client,there are several options for using the Linux(R) client using "
"FreeBSD's Linux Compatibility Layer."
msgstr "虽然 Steam 不提供原生的 FreeBSD 客户端，但有几个选项可以使用 FreeBSD 的 Linux 兼容层来使用 Linux(R) 客户端。"

#. type: Title ====
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/wine/_index.adoc:159
